### isKillAddress() {#a948d5bb1eccf928e50384305678340e7}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype="bool DbgAssignIntrinsic::isKillAddress () const">
<a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/check">Check</a> whether this kills the address component.

This doesn&#39;t take into account the position of the intrinsic, therefore a returned value of false does not guarentee the address is a valid location for the variable at the intrinsic&#39;s position in IR.
